title: mjNichols.Laced.Up.Drum.Kit
description:
The Laced Up Drum Kit is by mjNichols is for the producers who are looking upgrade their drum arsenal for 2015. Inspired by producers such as Metro Boomin, Sonny Digital and Zaytoven. This kit is perfect for those who are searching for the hardest hitting drums on the market. 

Details: 

100+ Unique Drum Samples and Loops 

6 808s 
10 Kicks 
14 Snares 
12 Claps 
11 Closed Hats 
6 Open Hats 
5 Cymbals 
19 Loops 
10 Percs 
14 Vox
 
http://www.mjnichols.net/
